### Backend — News Engine (Gemini Prompt)

#### [MODIFY] [news_engine.py](file:///e:/U_Hack_FormaOS-1/cloud_run/services/news_engine.py)

- Update `_slim_stats()` to include `birth_country` field (passed in from data manager).
- Update `INTEL_PROMPT` template to add a new context section:
  ```
  CONDIȚII METEO LA MECI (data {match_date}, {stadium_city}):
  {weather_json}
  
  CLIMAT DE ORIGINE (per jucător):
  {climate_context}
  ```
  Gemini is instructed to incorporate climate disadvantage in `physical_state` and elevate `overall_weakness_score` for highly disadvantaged players.
- Update `generate_pregame_intelligence_v2()` signature to accept `match_weather` and `climate_context` optional params.

