## Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    S[Settings Screen] -->|stadiumId + gameDate + matchTime| API1["/api/v1/pregame/match-weather"]
    API1 --> WE[weather_engine.py\nget_forecast_for_match lat,lng,datetime]
    WE -->|OWM /forecast| OWM[(OpenWeatherMap API)]
    OWM --> WE
    WE --> WeatherSnap[WeatherSnapshot dict]

    API2["/api/v1/pregame/opponent-weakness?game_date=..."] --> DM[data_manager.py]
    DM -->|players + birth_country| CE[climate_engine.py\nassess_climate_disadvantage]
    CE -->|climate_context| NE[news_engine.py\ngenerate_pregame_intelligence_v2]
    WeatherSnap --> NE
    NE -->|Gemini prompt with weather+climate| GEM[(Gemini AI)]
    GEM --> Players[List PlayerWeakness\n+ climate_danger field]
    Players --> Flutter[Pregame Screen\nWeather Banner + Climate Risk filter]
```

